  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <h1>Mix Vegetables</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="fruit-description">
      <p>
       Delight in the wholesome goodness of our carefully curated selection of fresh vegetables and roots, harvested at peak maturity to deliver rich flavor, vibrant color, and superior nutrition. From the earthy heartiness of Elephant Yam—ideal for robust curries and stir-fries—to the crisp, tender charm of Okra that brings life to every sauté or stew, our range offers something for every kitchen. Spice up your meals with fiery Green Chillies, handpicked for their intensity and aroma, or enjoy the nutritious depth of Drumsticks, perfect for traditional South Asian recipes. Add a zing of warmth with aromatic Ginger and the golden vibrance of Turmeric Root, both treasured for their flavor and healing benefits. Each item, including our fresh, crunchy Apples, is packaged with care and offered at competitive rates to ensure you receive farm-fresh quality that satisfies both your palate and your pocket.    
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <h1>Explore our offerings below</h1>
  </div>

  <!-- Product Sections -->

  <div class="section">
    <div class="image-container right">
      <img src="/image/fruits/suran.webp" alt="Elephant Yam">
    </div>
    <div class="text-container">
      <h2> Elephant Yam</h2>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> Large, starchy tubers with a mildly sweet flavor, perfect for curries, stir-fries, and soups.</p>
      <p><strong>Packaging:</strong> 10Kg Net and gross</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong>  Competitive pricing based on weight and quantity.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="text-container">
      <h2> Okra (Lady's Finger)</h2>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong>  Tender, green pods with a unique slimy texture when cooked, ideal for sautéing, frying, or adding to stews.</p>
      <p><strong>Packaging:</strong>  4Kg Box</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong> Affordable rates per kilogram or per dozen.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="image-container">
      <img src="/image/fruits/okra.webp" alt="Okra">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="image-container right">
      <img src="/image/fruits/green-chilli.webp" alt="Green Chillies">
    </div>
    <div class="text-container">
      <h2>Green Chilly</h2>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong>  Vibrant green peppers with varying degrees of heat, excellent for adding spice to dishes or pickling.</p>
      <p><strong>Packaging:</strong>  3.8Kg Net, 4.4Kg Gross (Premium Quality)</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong>   Competitive pricing based on heat level and quantity.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="text-container">
      <h2>  Drumsticks</h2>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong>   Long, slender pods with tender flesh and a slightly bitter taste, commonly used in South Asian and African cuisines</p>
      <p><strong>Packaging:</strong>  4Kg Net and Gross</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong>  Reasonably priced per unit or per kilogram</p>
    </div>
    <div class="image-container">
      <img src="/image/fruits/Drumstick.avif" alt="Drumsticks">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="image-container right">
      <img src="/image/spices/ginger.jpg" alt="Ginger">
    </div>
    <div class="text-container">
      <h2> Ginger</h2>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong>  Aromatic rhizomes with a spicy, slightly sweet flavor, versatile for use in both savory and sweet dishes.</p>
      <p><strong>Packaging:</strong>   4Kg Net</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong> Competitive rates based on weight and quality.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="text-container">
      <h2> Turmeric Root</h2>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong>  Bright orange rhizomes with a warm, earthy flavor and potent medicinal properties, perfect for seasoning and coloring dishes</p>
